{"tid":44461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"幸 福 天 倫 樂！大 美 人 李 嘉 欣 仔 仔 錫 老 公 寵！","createTime":"2016-12-18T10:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T16:06:13.000Z","uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cfbcbb43d0b88d67ad17c4890193ac98383e4d4","tid":44461,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"講幸福，一定離唔開大美人李嘉欣！06年，Michele雖然獲大劉以「The One」署名登全版廣告賀壽，但富商許晉亨已經開始對大美人展開追求。<br />\n<br />\n有Face有Money的亨亨，同大美人簡直天造地設，自動跑出！同李嘉欣08年結婚，11年仲有咗小JM Jayden Max Hui！一家樂也融融！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/173913_3c6ceddd41e49e1db782f049a4dce82b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F173913_3c6ceddd41e49e1db782f049a4dce82b.jpg&h=ce87ba63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AL5yd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AL5yd8.jpg&h=4eb257f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小JM今日已經識多國語言，仲入咗名校男拔小學，陪爸爸捉棋時，樣子仲十分專心可愛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/173915_d81371f920ac1078258c7e996c99405c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F173915_d81371f920ac1078258c7e996c99405c.jpg&h=e91fe360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過仔仔點都係鍾意痴住媽媽！大美人仲不時同仔仔共浴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/173915_967d65be5b8f4bda7903f761bf075fd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F173915_967d65be5b8f4bda7903f761bf075fd6.jpg&h=a2793966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5N7PCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5N7PCR.jpg&h=4b929d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/180046_8edb824b8a59c16c98123efb40e44fc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F180046_8edb824b8a59c16c98123efb40e44fc7.jpg&h=2d28682a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">I love my mum because she is pretty</span><br />\n</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98524618e18b113aa5fc71c643d87cf95564cf17","tid":44461,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"4cef07e0856111c6d6edd4cdffa0600dd875ff7a","tid":44461,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e30dd75fcff227522dc726cb1b26e915239e8d8","tid":44461,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/180046_8edb824b8a59c16c98123efb40e44fc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F180046_8edb824b8a59c16c98123efb40e44fc7.jpg&h=2d28682a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nMy mum's favourite thing to do is swearing. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.meme.am/cache/instances/folder587/53453587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?